      <h1>Refund & Cancellation Policy</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>We at <strong>Tranquil-Trips</strong> value our customers and strive to provide a pleasant booking experience. Our refund and cancellation policy ensures fairness and clarity for all users.</p>
      
      <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Bookings canceled <strong>within 24 hours</strong> of confirmation will be eligible for a full refund.</li>
        <li>Cancellations made <strong>7 days prior</strong> to the check-in date are eligible for a 50% refund.</li>
        <li>No refunds will be issued for cancellations made <strong>less than 7 days</strong> before check-in.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Refunds will be processed within <strong>5-7 business days</strong> from the cancellation confirmation.</li>
        <li>All refunds will be credited to the original payment method used during booking.</li>
        <li>Transaction fees or other non-refundable charges are excluded from the refund amount.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>For any issues or concerns, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@tranquiltrips.com">support@tranquiltrips.com</a>.</p>
